      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must use the same device geometry and operating conditions as the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under the same five operating points specified in the COU. Blood analog fluid properties matched COU conditions. Validation activities directly address the intended use scenario."
    },
