      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver convergence to residual tolerance of 1e-5 or better for all equations.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to residuals below 1e-6 for continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations. Convergence monitored via residual history and mass imbalance. No convergence anomalies observed across the five operating points."
    },
    {
