      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Test samples factor not required for assessment at Model Risk Level 2. Sample-to-sample variability in pump geometry manufacturing tolerances is addressed through the tolerance sensitivity analysis in the COU rather than through this credibility factor."
    },
